    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. they'll say the same stuff and then tomorrow it'll all be starting up again with the comments and the stares. it's just a cycle. i feel like if i could just find a way to actually make the noise go away for good, i could finally have some peace. like, a real way to just exit the situation. isn't it exhausting for you too, just having to keep pretending things are okay when they clearly aren't?",
